{"about_the_game":"You are the last soldier left on the battlefield.<br>Show your last bit of willpower to the enemy who is coming at you from both sides.<br>The game's most distinctive feature is the keyboard-banging controls, which make the battles all the more thrilling.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/extras/attack.gif?t=1725498445\" /><br>The direction of the attack changes depending on the key pressed on the keyboard.<br>The more keys pressed at the same time, the wider the attack range.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/extras/keyboard_e.jpg?t=1725498445\" /><br>A series of attacks adds a powerful attack.<br>Attacks also serve as movement.<br>At night, peddlers appear, and you can heal and power up by buying their goods.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/extras/shop_e.jpg?t=1725498445\" /><br>When the gauge is at its maximum, waving the mouse around activates a special move to wipe out the enemy.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/extras/special.gif?t=1725498445\" /><br>The more time passes, the stronger enemies appear, and there is always a sense of tension.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/extras/strong.jpg?t=1725498445\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1725498445","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1725498445","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1725498445","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2874130/capsule_